Package: findpoolreg
Type: Package
Title: Find Pooling Region for Precipitation Extremes
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Leandra Zanger
Maintainer: Leandra Zanger <Leandra.Zanger@hhu.de>
Description: Parametric bootstrap test for assessing whether precipitation 
    extremes of a set of locations are homogeneous w.r.t. their Generalised
    Extreme Value distribution.
